summary: This code is archiving the "agi_computer_control" directory, removing the original 7z file, and moving a backup copy into the directory.

details.comment: This code is archiving the "agi_computer_control" directory, removing the original 7z file, and moving a backup copy into the directory.
details.content:
rm agi_computer_control.7z
cd ..
7z a -snl agi_computer_control.7z agi_computer_control
cd agi_computer_control
mv ../agi_computer_control.7z .
